Re: Getting job at Vanguard Charlotte Office?


Quote


Postby carolinaman » Sun Sep 08, 2013 6:00 am 
I do not know for sure all the functions and services Vanguard has in Charlotte. I do know they have a sizable technology unit and I met a guy this spring who manages a wealth management group based in Charlotte. They also have a call center. It sounds like they may be opportunities for you there. Best wishes.


